OL,3,CDeath of toddler Xielo Maruziva who
OL,4,Cdrowned in River Soar 'accidental'
OL,6,FThe death of a two-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdrowned in the River Soar in
OL,8,FLeicestershire was an "accident", an
OL,9,Finquest jury has concluded.
OL,11,FXielo Maruziva went missing after
OL,12,Fgoing into the water in the Aylestone
OL,13,FMeadows nature reserve, close to
OL,14,FMarsden Lane in February 2024.
OL,16,FThe toddler died after going for a
OL,17,Fwalk with his aunts at the nature
OL,18,Freserve.
