OL,3,CDeath of toddler Xielo Maruziva who
OL,4,Cdrowned in River Soar 'accidental'
OL,6,FHis body was found nearly four months
OL,7,Flater in the area after specialist
OL,8,Fsearches were carried out.
OL,10,FAt the time of the search, his family
OL,11,Fhad described him as a "cheeky, funny"
OL,12,Fboy and "a bundle of joy," and thanked
OL,13,Fmembers of the community for their
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,16,FAt City Hall in Leicester on Thursday,
OL,17,Fthe coroner praised emergency services
OL,18,Ffor their swift response.
