OL,4,Cdrowned in River Soar 'accidental'
OL,6,FThe inquest at City Hall in Leicester
OL,7,Fhad already heard from Leicestershire
OL,8,FPolice, who said CCTV footage from the
OL,9,Fscene showed that Xielo had been for a
OL,10,Fwalk with his aunt and great aunt on
OL,11,Fthe day he disappeared.
OL,13,FDI Kevin Hames from the force told the
OL,14,Finquest he said he wasn't able to
OL,15,Fconfirm the distance between the two-
OL,16,Fyear-old and his two aunts when he
OL,17,Fwent into the water.
