OL,6,FAt the time of the disappearance, he
OL,7,Ftold the inquest a "full scale multi-
OL,8,Fagency response'" was deployed, with
OL,9,Fthe rescue operation being led by
OL,10,FLeicestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService, and police being responsible
OL,12,Ffor the "recovery" part of the
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FSpecialist paramedics, volunteers,
OL,16,Fdrones, dogs were all deployed,
OL,17,Falongside voluntary teams including
OL,18,Fthe Leicester Search and Rescue Team.
